Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.56,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,It’s here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.18,N_Har,Haruna,0000,0000,0000,,These are pretty cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:09.60,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,I know, huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.48,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,You think that’s cool…?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.26,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:17.91,N_Nod,Nodoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes; I concur!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:19.63,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:28.02,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san, um… we don’t have to wear these clothes as Chupa Team members, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:33.83,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What’re you talking about? That’s why I made them in the first place! We gotta wear it everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:35.64,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,I will not wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:39.62,N_Set,,0000,0000,0000,,And I refuse to see Ojou-sama wear it, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:46.63,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, this is awesome! Secchan, try one on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:48.23,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ojou-sama…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.34,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Ane-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:54.02,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did you make so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:58.05,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the more stuff we make, the cheaper our tankers will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:01:00.11,N_FF,Shichimi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder ‘bout that, mya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:05.67,N_Har,Motsu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are people who stay in their pond and never know of the ocean. In a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:08.87,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? You saying you got a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:13.88,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Ane-san, even if those tankers end up being cheaper, would you be able to compensate them even if you can’t sell all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:18.85,N_FF,Shichimi,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to be freaked out, mya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:21.11,N_Har,Motsu,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it’s one of those moments where you gotta be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:28.60,N_Chi,Chisame,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:37.75,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Always busy, eh? This is the lodging house of Mahora Academy’s middle school division, Grade 9, Class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:39.64,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I showed up on the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:41.45,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:42.94,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:16.90,N_Say,,0000,0000,0000,,by Sayo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.62,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take attendance now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:22.39,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.61,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi Yuuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:26.58,N_Yuu,Yuuna,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.34,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I got skipped again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.62,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asakura Kazumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.00,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,…Asakura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.85,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, yeah, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.43,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Still tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:41.81,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:46.93,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Um… next is… Ayase Yue-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.15,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,I’m here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.35,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi Ako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:50.55,N_Ako,Ako,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.55,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Ookouchi Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:53.60,N_Aki,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.10,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Kakizaki Misa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.60,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,It gets pretty lonely, but you can’t do much about it when no one can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.03,N_Say,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.05,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,But you can see me, can’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.75,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.17,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:20.28,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? What is it, Asakura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.11,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been on my mind since I was in the 7th grade, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.93,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the seat next to me always empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.23,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.73,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.78,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, but give me a bit more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:34.50,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.30,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I’ll be able to talk to you properly about it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:50.06,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(189,350)}A deep fog, I seek…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:50.06,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,0)\pos(471,350)}The shadow seen only by closed eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.06,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,0)\pos(360,392)}the voice heard only by closed ears…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:54.42,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(237,392)}Cut through the fog
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.42,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(492,0)\pos(453,392)}and appear before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.82,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(283,392)}Tel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.82,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(311,0)\pos(328,392)}Ma
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:58.82,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(476,0)\pos(396,392)}Amoris!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.67,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I can see them! I can see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:12.18,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamichi, look! Spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.68,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,You can see ‘em? Good job, Negi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:18.52,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,You finally got the result of studying half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.37,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all thanks to you, Takamichi-sensei. Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.09,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:31.68,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Eva-san! I gotta go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:35.00,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Imbecile. I wasn’t complimenting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:41.18,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Master is glad that she can finally return to her peaceful living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.24,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. Every evening, there's an intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:49.37,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that. We cannot afford to train magic in public after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.17,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Why me, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.95,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,This place makes me calm, that’s why.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.82,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you’re such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.18,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not scare my master’s character.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:03.27,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,If you are to say, say “this place fails to make me calm…”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.25,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,That’s also a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.03,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Then, say “This place is disgusting…”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.01,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to be dismantled, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:15.10,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(237,392)}Cut through the fog
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.10,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(419,0)\pos(453,392)}and appear before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:17.46,N_Spells,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,0)\pos(283,392)}Tel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.46,N_Spells,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(320,0)\pos(327,392)}Ma
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:17.46,N_Spells,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,0)\pos(396,392)}Amoris!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:29.95,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo-san? You’re Aisaka Sayo-san, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.89,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah… um…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:35.09,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I can see you! I’m finally able to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:39.17,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a pleasure to meet you. I’m the homeroom teacher, Negi Springfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:42.42,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Though… It’s probably weird that I’m saying “pleasure to meet you” and all…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:49.54,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Can you… can you really see me, Negi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.55,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:06:59.58,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a pleasure to meet you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.24,N_Nat,Natsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Uwaaah…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:08.72,N_Chi,Chizuru,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, what a bad hobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.17,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.85,N_Nat,Natsumi,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, you want us to buy this..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:17.50,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,I made a bit too much. Since we’re friends and all… I beg of you, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:23.34,N_Chi,Chizuru,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, in regards to stuff like this, I don’t need anything, so… Natsumi, you buy something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.10,N_Nat,Natsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.47,N_Nat,Natsumi,0000,0000,0000,,W-wait a second, Chizu-nee! Why am I the only one buying something here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:33.99,N_Chi,Chizuru,0000,0000,0000,,Natsumi, the structure of society is not as easy as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.56,N_Chi,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, you’ll understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.23,N_Nat,Natsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ehhhhh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.91,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why am I a ghost, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:47.51,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. People seem to think that one becomes a ghost only when one has any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:53.05,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why, if we can solve your leftover memories, you’ll be able to rest in peace…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.47,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good idea, Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.76,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that stuff in the Magic Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.23,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Leftover memories…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:08.59,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Remainder of thought, called a Spirit. That’s what my teacher said when I was still in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:15.14,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also told that spirits tend to have leftover feelings that are more on the emotional and painful side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:24.71,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I know you may not want to share the details, but I want to help you! I want you to rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:33.03,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei, I’m happy and all, but I’m afraid I’m unable to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.37,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.48,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.79,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Were your memories that painful…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.05,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:48.10,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just that I don’t remember anything from when I was living!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:54.13,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that I forgot my memories during the 40 years I’ve spent being a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:05.31,N_Yuu,Yuuna,0000,0000,0000,,Unit of Hell, we have come to greet! Compassion is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.21,N_Yuu,Yuuna,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:09.69,N_Yuu,Yuuna,0000,0000,0000,,Nipaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:13.56,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuna, this is awesome! Well made!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:14.36,N_Yuu,Yuuna,0000,0000,0000,,I know, huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:19.02,N_Yuu,Yuuna,0000,0000,0000,,This whole thing took me a week to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.82,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter hobby, isn’t it..?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.43,N_Ako,Ako,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna, your Oolong tea’s done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:25.65,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thank you{\fnArial}~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.47,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,…the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.06,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ako’s hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.10,N_Ako,Ako,0000,0000,0000,,Lab instruments are so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.33,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,What another bitter hobby this is…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.38,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Ako; buy a T-shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.19,N_Ako,Ako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don’t need one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.03,N_Yuu,Yuuna,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll pass on that offer, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:44.42,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!? But aren’t you a member!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.86,N_Yuu,Yuuna,0000,0000,0000,,I was free on those days, so I just decided to take a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:50.17,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Won’t you buy one? I’ll make a special discount, soo please{\fnArial}~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.31,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,I told you they wouldn’t sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.71,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,What’d you say you little…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.58,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,ANIMAL ABUSE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.93,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,You can sense something in the Girls’ Dorm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.69,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:09.63,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s the case, there may be something in there that’ll help you regain your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.21,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.56,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I’ll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.46,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wait, Sayo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.14,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.91,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hotline?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.81,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Hold this between your door, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:29.55,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever something happens, you can contact me ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.95,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it’s a string phone, de gozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.17,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of this when Kaede-san said something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:40.35,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,Since we’re in the opposite room, I figured we should take advantage of this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:43.53,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,I see… A hotline, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:48.59,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I can be in contact with you 24 hours a day! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.33,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Secchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:51.51,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.41,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,A string phone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:58.86,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaede-san! Can you say a little something through this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.84,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,“A little something,” de gozaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:06.87,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,Wo-tay ets-say of rog-fay roaks-cay ake-may ix-say roaks-cay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:09.02,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I can hear it! It’s perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.85,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:11.56,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,But you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:15.59,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,The sound went away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.07,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Secchan, this is the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:24.33,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,If the door’s on the string, you won’t be able to hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.94,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,A... A BLIND SPOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:29.23,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Secchan, you’re silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.85,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah{\fnArial}~ {\fnOldTypefaces}Oh my gosh{\fnArial}~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:34.04,N_Kon,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:37.05,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I got separated from Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.57,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no{\fnArial}~ {\fnOldTypefaces}What should I do{\fnArial}~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:52.36,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo-san! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.35,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.72,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? And who’s “Sayo?”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:02.91,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… um… You see… What was it…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:04.68,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:05.86,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.19,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Negima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:14.36,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,There was a ghost in here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:18.39,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… a weird voice came out of the string phone…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:19.74,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,String phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.93,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um… Long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.77,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, where’s the ghost? Did it disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.41,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it, de gozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.54,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.73,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost in the Girls’ Dorm…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.10,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s the case, I’ll just have to use magic to find Sayo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.39,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(295,392)}Rastel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:42.39,N_Spells,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(412,0)\pos(389,392)}Mascir…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.53,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:48.73,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,How suspicious! You’re not hiding something, are you, Negi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.09,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,No! Of course I’m not…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:54.27,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t something the Journalism Club is gonna let slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.10,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:02.63,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,I placed orders to the Yukihiro Group Merchandising Club to produce...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:06.34,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,Customized Negi-sensei alarm clocks in which the alarm is Negi-sensei’s voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:10.74,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei cups so you can see Negi-sensei’s smiling face when you’re done drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:15.42,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei toasters that imprint Negi-sensei’s face on the toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.59,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,Etcetera, etcetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.75,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, this is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.48,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Though I’m used to all of this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:26.73,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I’ll always be with Negi-sensei everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:32.85,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,, In such beautiful living, why, why would I want to include this indecent thing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.04,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t call me “indecent!”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.84,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,You’re plenty indecent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.78,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,BIGGER ANIMAL ABUSE!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.06,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Asuna, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:48.36,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Maki-chan, how can you be so comfortable wearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:52.86,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I didn’t wear this, then Iinchou-san wouldn’t acknowledge me as a fellow classmate, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:59.05,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, Asuna-san. Try someone else. I’m never going to buy any of your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:02.27,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!? C’mon, buy a Chupa Tee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.03,N_Mak,Makie’s Tongue,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,350)}MAH!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:10.78,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I’ve been revived! Too bad I’m dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.39,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,T-t-t-t-t-that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.32,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.22,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I’m… imagining things…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.64,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Learn to get a grip, Makie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.39,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Chupa Tee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:23.42,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:29.30,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is a big scoop! Why did Aisaka Sayo, Mahora Academy’s neighborhood ghost, die!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:32.54,N_Kaz,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly happened 40 years ago!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:36.77,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,I’m burnin’! I’m burnin’ up here! My Journalism Club spirit’s flarin’ up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.63,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asakura-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:41.66,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for explaining, Negi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.53,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,The mystery’s been solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:46.73,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know that the empty seat next to me actually seated a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.75,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why there wasn’t such thing written in the students’ record book, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:55.51,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll explain this to the whole class someday, but for now, please keep it a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:56.32,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:02.55,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-kun, that’s against freedom of the press! We have the right to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.68,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,So when the chance comes, I’ll tell it to the class-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.91,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.43,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.59,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki-san! Lingshen-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.71,N_Sat,Yotsuba,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.46,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,The ghost! Did it show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.55,N_Lin,Chao,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.85,N_Sat,Yotsuba,0000,0000,0000,,So is it really a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.28,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.15,N_Lin,Chao,0000,0000,0000,,There was an accident on the meat bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.20,N_2,Kazumi and Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Meat bun…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.86,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I stole some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.42,N_Aki,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Is that good, Yamamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.03,N_Kas,Misora,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yamamoto domesticated?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.51,N_Aki,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,A bit. Right, Yamamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:53.81,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,So this fish’s name is Yamamoto-san? How interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:55.87,N_Kas,Misora,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.14,N_Aki,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,I feel… a shiver going down my spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.75,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I-I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:04.46,N_Aki,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Misora?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:07.08,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I’m so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.62,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-san! Misora-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.14,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a ghost here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.14,N_Aki,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:18.87,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, son-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.19,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:25.08,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,I’m back…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.79,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, welcome back! Were you able to sell any T-shirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.68,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see here…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:32.39,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this society…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:34.86,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,What another exaggerated reaction…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:38.65,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way. Asuna, there was a ghost here earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.14,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:43.53,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Ojou-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:46.44,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,The ghost showed up in another room, too, de gozaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:47.01,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:49.22,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei is currently pursuing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.48,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-kun is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:51.98,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Then let’s get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.91,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya mean, “ghost?”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:58.46,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t think of that sort of stuff at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:08.26,N_Nod,Nodoka,0000,0000,0000,,How cute…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.03,N_FF,Shichimi,0000,0000,0000,,Mya{\fnArial}~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.46,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka, you just took a bath; you’ll catch its hairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.25,N_Nod,Nodoka,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.07,N_Nod,Nodoka,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:26.33,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so good at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.20,N_Har,Haruna,0000,0000,0000,,Yue! Nodoka!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.40,N_Kuu,Kuu Fei,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, aru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:34.56,N_2,Yue and Nodoka,0000,0000,0000,,Gho...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:36.77,N_2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gho...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.02,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.72,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I went through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.23,N_2,Chisame and Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,Wintermute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.75,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm, nummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.56,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Does this look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:12.97,N_Zaz,Zazie,0000,0000,0000,,Zazie’s outfit… is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.54,N_Man,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,You suspicious intruder…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.84,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:18.89,N_Man,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:23.40,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Mana-san, STOP! STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:39.91,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I’m very sorry… I was just so happy that I started to go off and play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:41.34,N_Neg,Nego,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.15,N_Har,Haruna,0000,0000,0000,,So she’s over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:45.26,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t really see her, though…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.03,N_FF,Twins,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:47.39,N_FF,,0000,0000,0000,,Desu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.87,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,It’s alright; she’s not scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:55.49,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,She was just playing around tonight; she didn’t mean to cause any harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.94,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say she isn’t scary…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:02.65,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t even know what she looks like, so we can’t really understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:05.90,N_Chi,Chizuru,0000,0000,0000,,For all we know, she could be a dreadful figure…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.92,N_2,All,0000,0000,0000,,Freaky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.05,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t good…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:15.23,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,If only I can at least get her in a picture…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:25.95,N_Kaz,Kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,It showed up! It showed up! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:28.16,N_2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.02,N_Kuu,Kuu Fei,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:31.00,N_FF,Twin,0000,0000,0000,,she’s just a regular girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.80,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,You… can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.25,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right! I showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:38.56,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,But how…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.48,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Eva-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.61,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Master
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:49.32,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,It’s so noisy there. I’m gonna go back and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.30,N_Cha,Cha,0000,0000,0000,,You slept this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:54.08,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,So I’ve been raised as a sleeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:04.86,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And so, all’s well that ends well for the ghost, who has even made friends with Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.83,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Have you regained any of your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:10.66,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.68,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry for causing such a ruckus earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:19.12,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be! Thanks to you, I was able to introduce you to the rest of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.23,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:26.81,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo-san, take your time; no need to confuse yourself. You have plenty of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:31.78,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! If I remember anything, I’ll report it to you, Negi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:32.75,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:36.03,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,And until then, I’ll be in your care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.30,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:46.04,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:47.59,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.58,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Be seated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:51.55,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take attendance now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.11,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka Sayo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:56.06,N_Say,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.14,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Who’s she?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:48.48,N_FF,Twins,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! We’re the Narutaki Twins who always get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:49.72,N_FF,Fuuka,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Fuuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:51.26,N_FF,Fumika,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Fumika!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:52.59,N_FF,Twins,0000,0000,0000,,Remember us, ‘kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:57.39,N_FF,Twins,0000,0000,0000,,Next time! “Sensei, turn us into adults, please!”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:10.23,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.36,0:23:14.47,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone marched already!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:17.25,N_Mac,Machine,0000,0000,0000,,Good Morning, Baka Pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:21.73,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Court Lady, good morning! I’m sorry I’m late!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:23.84,N_Mac,Machine,0000,0000,0000,,I have orders for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:24.01,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:31.06,N_Mac,Machine,0000,0000,0000,,Potatoes, carrots, onions, and ah, we’re out of milk, so get some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:33.88,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,A person for errands, am I..?
